"VT ES01AB","Eastern Storm Adventure Bag","<b>Adventure Bags</b><BR>At their most basic function, adventure bags are bags intended to store and carry your dice. However, these are much more than a couple pieces of felt with a drawstring. For one thing, every bag is made from high-quality materials. The outer shell of every bag is suede moleskin fabric with a satin liner. Metal eyelets, satin drawstrings and beaded pulls are all chosen to complement the design that graces the inside of every adventure bag. <BR><BR><b>Rolling on the Bag</b><BR>Of course, there are other pretty dice bags out there. What makes adventure bags truly unique is that they are not simply intended for carrying dice. When opened all the way, adventure bags provide a flat surface and raised edge where you can roll dice, so you can control your dice wherever your game is played. And since the bags open wide, you'll never have to search through your bag blindly - just open the bag and select the dice you want.<BR><BR><B><I>*Note:</I></B> These adventure bags will hold up to 50 dice.<BR><BR><div align=""center""><img src=""http://www.boardgamelifestyle.com/images/easternstorm.jpg"" width=""250"" vspace=5><BR><img src=""http://www.boardgamelifestyle.com/images/easternstorm1.jpg"" width=""250"" vspace=5></div>","easternstorm.jpg","",26.90,2,0.60,1999-11-30 00:00:00,2009-02-07 00:00:00,"VixenTor",Active,0,0,2009,N,0.00,N,0,0,0,"Accessories",,,,,,,
